## Back Matter: Index & About the Author

### Pages 341–350: Index (S–Z)

These pages are the book's back-matter index. No substantive content —
index entries only, listing page references for topics and names
covered throughout the book. Notable index entries confirm key themes:

- **Socialism** — entries span capitalism's replacement, proletariat,
  Utopian vs. scientific, Veblen's views
